&lt;p&gt;At GiveDirectly, we are always looking for talented, deeply &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.givedirectly.org/givedirectly-values/&quot;&gt;values-aligned&lt;/a&gt; folks to join our team. Opportunities to work at GiveDirectly may open up throughout the year, and our goal is to find the best people as quickly as we can.&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;This post is not a job opening; &lt;/em&gt;however, when a new role opens, we often begin our hiring search within our own database as a first step.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Learn more about our teams:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
