&lt;p&gt;This year, we’re focused on ensuring direct cash and GiveDirectly are gaining fast, targeted visibility and understanding among high value audiences. Two of our main tools for doing this are earned media coverage and collaborations with influencers, surrogates, thought leaders.&lt;/p&gt;
